quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  76,1,"Hel eta alelﾂｴinsani hﾄｱynﾃｼm mined dehri lem yekun ﾅ歹yﾂｴen mezkura"
  76,2,"ﾄｰnna halaknelﾂｴinsane min nutfetin emﾅ歛cin nebteliyhi feceﾂｴalnahu semiyﾂｴan basﾄｱyra"
  76,3,"ﾄｰnna hedeynahussebiyle imma ﾅ歛kirav ve imma kefura"
  76,4,"ﾄｰnna aﾂｴtedna lilkafiriyne selasile ve aﾄ殕alen ve seﾂｴﾄｱyren"
  76,5,"ﾄｰnnelﾂｴebrare yeﾅ殲ebune min keﾂｴsin kane mizacuha kafura"
  75,20,"Kella bel tuhﾄｱbbunelﾂｴacilete"
  75,21,"Ve tezerunelﾂｴahﾄｱrete"
  75,22,"Vucuhun yevmeizin nadﾄｱretun"
  75,23,"ﾄｰla rabbiha nazﾄｱretun"
  75,24,"Ve vucuhun yevmeizin basireﾂｴun"
  75,25,"Tezunnu en yufﾂｴale biha fakﾄｱretun"
  75,26,"Kella iza beleﾄ歛titterakﾄｱye"
  75,27,"Ve kﾄｱyle men rakﾄｱn"
  75,28,"Ve zanne ennehulfraku"
  75,29,"Velteffetissaku bissakﾄｱ"
  75,30,"ﾄｰla rabbike yevmeizinilmesaku"
  75,31,"Fela saddeka ve la salla"
  75,32,"Ve lakin kezzebe ve tevella"
  75,33,"Summe zehebe ila ehlihi yetemetta"
  75,34,"Evla leke feevla"
  75,35,"Summe evlaleke feevla"
  75,36,"Eyahsebulﾂｴinsanu en yutreke suden"
  75,37,"Elem yeku nutfeten min meniyyin yumna"
  75,38,"Summe kane ﾂｴalekaten fehaleka fesevva"
  75,39,"Feceﾂｴale minhuzzeyceynizzekere velﾂｴunsa"
  75,40,"Eleyse zalike bikadirin ﾂｴala en yuhyiyelmevra"
